<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Why Software Engineering? - Boot Camp Invitation</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        --primary: #3b82f6;
        --primary-dark: #2563eb;
        --secondary: #6366f1;
        --bg-light: #f8fafc;
        --text-dark: #1e293b;
        --text-light: #f8fafc;
        --success: #10b981;
        --warning: #f59e0b;
        --error: #ef4444;
      }

      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      }

      body {
        background-color: var(--bg-light);
        color: var(--text-dark);
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem 1rem;
      }

      header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }

      header h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        color: var(--primary);
      }

      header p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: var(--text-dark);
        opacity: 0.8;
      }

      .card {
        background-color: white;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        padding: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
      }

      .section-title {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        color: var(--primary);
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
        border-bottom: 2px solid var(--primary-dark);
      }

      .session-list {
        margin: 1.5rem 0;
      }

      .session-list li {
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        position: relative;
        padding-left: 1.5rem;
      }

      .session-list li::before {
        content: 'â€¢';
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        color: var(--primary);
        font-size: 1.2rem;
      }

      .zoom-button {
        display: block;
        background-color: var(--primary);
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 1rem 2rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        margin: 2rem auto;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        width: fit-content;
      }

      .zoom-button:hover {
        background-color: var(--primary-dark);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
      }

      .highlight {
        background-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin: 1.5rem 0;
        border-left: 4px solid var(--primary);
      }

      .date-time {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        background-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
        padding: 1rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin: 1.5rem 0;
      }

      .date-time-label {
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--success);
      }

      .date-time-value {
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      @media (max-width: 640px) {
        header h1 {
          font-size: 2rem;
        }
        
        .date-time {
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: flex-start;
          gap: 0.5rem;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <header>
        <h1>Why Software Engineering?</h1>
        <p>Boot Camp Invitation</p>
      </header>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="highlight">
          <p>Thanks for registering for the "Why Software Engineering?" Boot Camp! We're thrilled you're joining us. Since spots are limited, please confirm your participation ASAP to lock in your seat.</p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="section-title">Online Session</h2>
        <ul class="session-list">
          <li><strong>Business Analysis:</strong> Turn business ideas into killer software solutions</li>
          <li><strong>UI/UX Design:</strong> Dream up the perfect solution design</li>
          <li><strong>Project Management:</strong> Nail down your project plan</li>
          <li><strong>LinkedIn:</strong> Polish up your profile to shine</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="section-title">Physical Session</h2>
        <ul class="session-list">
          <li><strong>GitHub Crash Course:</strong> Master version control like a pro</li>
          <li><strong>Development:</strong> Bring your software solution to life</li>
          <li><strong>QA:</strong> Test like a tech wizard</li>
          <li><strong>DevOps:</strong> Deploy your solution with ease</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="date-time">
          <div>
            <span class="date-time-label">Date:</span>
            <span class="date-time-value">March 26th</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="date-time-label">Time:</span>
            <span class="date-time-value">7:30 PM</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="date-time-label">Platform:</span>
            <span class="date-time-value">Zoom</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p>Our first session is on March 26th at 7:30 PM on Zoom. Confirm your spot, and let's make this journey epic!</p>

        <a href="https://plymouth.zoom.us/j/96211638956" class="zoom-button" target="_blank">
          Join Zoom Meeting
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
